{"type": "article", "id": 61874, "title": "一组极简风格的无绳灯，重现烛光的亲密感｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-07T23:30:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57135, "name": "Lady Technologies"}, {"id": 57136, "name": "SOPH."}, {"id": 46729, "name": "DRx Romanelli"}, {"id": 41489, "name": "Case Studyo"}, {"id": 44025, "name": "WUU"}, {"id": 57137, "name": "Voltra"}, {"id": 57138, "name": "James Jarvis"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190307211042eiWN9YpM3Z40w51z.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} </style>  </p><h3>Cordless Lighting by Voltra</h3><p>Voltra 是一个全新的照明品牌，来自香港，其推出的第一个系列 Cordless 是三款极简风格的无绳灯，意在重现烛光的亲密感。</p><p>Cordless 系列适用于家庭或餐厅用餐，提供柔和、大气的照明效果。设计师表示：”我们希望这款灯可以照亮周围人的面孔，鼓励大家进行对话和互动。”</p><p>整个系列有三款灯：Alabaster，Reeded 和 Frosted 。Alabaster 是用天然雪花石膏手工制作而成，每个灯都有独特的图案，呼应“华丽的艺术装饰风格的室内设计”。Reeded 将黄铜网与聚碳酸酯外层结合在一起，算是对传统煤气灯的重新想象。Frosted 是一种简约的半透明设计。</p><p>三个台灯均由电池供电，有两种不同尺寸。较大的，为大尺寸桌子设计，而较小的，则用于私密用餐。</p><p>Alabaster 和 Frosted 有四种不同颜色的底座：古铜色，天然黄铜，抛光铬和缎镍。Reeded 可选择青铜或天然黄铜的纹理底座。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211115k0Q8q3jtciMxdwZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211116cWU5jBMFgCJ84Ewh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211116RZMbzlq5s2Khnjpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211116vBnuil76YNk5xzcs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903072111169wNzjCuGp70nrHyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903072111154gyFrI85qH0nPTZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607445\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.voltralighting.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Voltra</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>逻辑茶几 &amp; 片段墙架 by WUU</h3><p>2019 是独立设计品牌 WUU 参展设计上海的第四年，继续在家具领域尝试探索，推出新品“逻辑茶几”和“片段墙架”。</p><p>两款新品延续了 WUU 一贯以来的设计风格，垂直与平行、交汇与分离，金属体块之间的相互关系，通过榫卯结构的嵌合构筑成具有美感的桌体支撑，整个系列包括三款适宜多种场景的功能茶几。严丝合缝的整体形态与精致的金色 PVD 表面处理，是 WUU 对美感与功能再度探索后的简练表达。</p><p>片段墙架也是由简练的几何体块构成。墙架主体表面不见任何锁定螺丝，亦可稳固于墙面并可达到 10kg+的承重。片段墙架提供 1.5 米和 1.2 米两种玻璃长度可选，适用于更多使用场景，即便在不置物品的情况也可以是非常美观的墙面装饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211553jAHwUdOspB1meS6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211533wuSYoM0DgiETvRer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211536RMDK6lV7QFf5UzWN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211621DLq9r6xbutyp7GPI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.539000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TEAPOT by James Jarvis &amp; Case Studyo</h3><p>最近，英国艺术家 James Jarvis 与创意机构 Case Studyo 合作推出联名企划，这次的限定作品取名为“TEAPOT”，顾名思义是将艺术家最具代表性的卡通形象 Sphere 转变成了茶壶。</p><p>这款高约 18 厘米的作品除了采用釉面瓷器打造之外，其中一只弯曲的手臂作为把手，另一只手作为壶嘴，而顶部的帽子则是壶盖。据悉这款 TEAPOT 仅限定发售 250 个，且每个都有限量编号。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903072116396ZCTw9h4slYB8XxS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211639OmX5I1qzLEpryPFK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://casestudyo.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Case Studyo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Modernica Eiffel Side Shell Chair by SOPH. &amp; DRx Romanelli</h3><p>最近，潮牌 SOPH. 与擅长旧物改造的设计师品牌 DRx Romanelli 合作，共同创造了一系列 Modernica Eiffel Side Shell Chair。</p><p>作为全新“ SOPH. For The Room ”家居企划的首个项目，整个系列一共带来 20 张独一无二的改造款贝壳椅，设计上将来自 F.C.R.B. 和 Nike 的复古单品，以及复古军事布料缝制于座椅表面，因此每张椅子都是独一无二。</p><p>整个系列贝壳椅将于 3 月 11 日在 SOPH. 线上店铺正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211729ilLAXWcVjuEgBCt6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019030721172921Phb376dr0FiZlw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211729Ut79mx6Hn5B4K3lr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211730jXK9HVxCvQPLehb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211730aB4MfGJ5OWIdVvbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903072117304Pgtzn6MwuLeX8WE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211730QhNDwysecVablrnR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211731HmAs5Tx9y7Q4EOVe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211731WXEpSDMT3CU2P70Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211731HTAEGfDcOhB4dvUq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kegg Kegel ball by Lady Technologies</h3><p>旧金山初创公司 Lady Technologies 推出了一款名为 Kegg 的可穿戴设备，可以用来测量宫颈粘液，提供较普通产品更为准确的生育预测率。</p><p>用户只需将 Kegg Kegel 球插入阴道内读取和分析女性的宫颈粘液，观察其在排卵周期中的粘度变化，两分钟即可读取数据。</p><p>这款装置通过骨盆底肌肉的收缩固定到位，这意味着它可以用于训练和强化肌肉，比如产妇产前产后常做的凯格尔运动。Kegg 包含一个压力传感器，通过内部振动电机和外部应用程序为用户提供有关其 Kegel 练习的即时反馈。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211809tiDXpTPJyoG4E2IH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211809cJIxd8wpK1O5Xi36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211810T3goCLIF42VMdcj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211810cHrnp4mGPAMOZt2z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211810Gwbd3mclNxjeOkIL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190307211809d2SPNHmweDYKJCxU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/03/06/kegg-kegel-ball-fertility-tracking-tech/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}